'''富拉'''（{{lang-ar|الفولة}}）是[[苏丹|苏丹]][[西科尔多凡州|西科尔多凡州]]的首府。

中国人对在富拉建设一个发电站和730千米长的输油管表示出兴趣。<ref name="Foster2009">{{cite book|last=Foster|first=Vivien|title=Building bridges: China's growing role as infrastructure financier for Sub-Saharan Africa|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=HzIslxyu6U4C&pg=PA28|accessdate=15 April 2013|year=2009|publisher=World Bank Publications|isbn=978-0-8213-7555-6|page=28}}</ref><ref name="China Rights Forum">{{cite book|title=China Rights Forum|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=8AQkAQAAIAAJ|accessdate=15 April 2013|year=2005|publisher=Human Rights in China, Incorporated}}</ref> 

[[第二次苏丹内战|第二次苏丹内战]]的冲突导致许多居民无家可归。<ref name="Deng1995">{{cite book|last=Deng|first=Francis M.|title=War of Visions: Conflicts of Identities in the Sudan|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=_g2TSlsi_G4C&pg=PA292|accessdate=15 April 2013|year=1995|publisher=Brookings Institution Press|isbn=978-0-8157-2369-1|page=292}}</ref> 

它是[[西科尔多凡大学|西科尔多凡大学]]所在地。

